@niji87 wrote:

It isn’t that hard to start coding on high revisions… I started with Matrix >.>
I messed with matrix for a bit and got tired of it since i wanted to make a server that is more like real runescape, so now I am using dementhium which is a lot easier than most people think.
I guess what I am trying to say is if you are determined to making a high detailed server, you can do it without starting with the 317 or 562 revisions.
If you have any questions or need help with dementhium or matrix, I will be glad to help you with what I can.
